ed grated Parmesan and garnish with basil leaves before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can replace the chicken thigh fillets with chicken breast in this recipe.","Please refer to <em>The Basic Cookbook <\/em>or <em>Everyday Cookbook<\/em> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","40m","4 portions"]}